Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.77,0:00:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial Black\pos(316,325)\fad(400,0)}Obey the Rules and manners\Nto have a fun Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.52,0:00:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sometime ago, for the sake of living, we left behind our happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.46,0:00:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We deceived ourselves, clinging to this mere illusion as we danced...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.71,0:00:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With closed eyes, at the end of the horizon,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.01,0:00:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was searching for your smiling face...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.52,0:00:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We embrace our dreams and continue on...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.48,0:00:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}within the swaying traces of memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.37,0:01:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Someday, I will once again grasp hold of
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.50,0:01:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}these feelings I have locked away in my heart... Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.56,0:01:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Rafael... As I thought, you were wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.36,0:01:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You shouldn't have used The Barrier of Orichalcos.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.57,0:01:42.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You turned your precious Monster into an evil form...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.12,0:01:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Was sending her to the Graveyard also a part of Dartz's so-called "destiny"?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.71,0:01:49.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In that case, I will change destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.42,0:01:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will smash the darkness of your heart with this card!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.30,0:02:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Destroy the Darkness of the Heart!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.19,0:02:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.98,0:02:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.20,0:02:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.46,0:02:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A cemetery!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.62,0:02:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that I activated a Magic Card called Underworld - Heaven Circle that lets us Summon Monsters from the Graveyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.09,0:02:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But this is a {\i0}real{\i1} graveyard...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.77,0:02:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rafael!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.53,0:02:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That boy is....
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.45,0:03:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rafael!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.09,0:03:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Rafael!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.89,0:03:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rafael...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.43,0:03:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These tombstones belong to my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.02,0:03:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.82,0:03:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dartz!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.07,0:03:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is... that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.49,0:03:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me... This is your memory?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.54,0:03:51.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Regardless of how far you may run, it shall remain the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.21,0:03:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rafael, no matter how far you may run, you shall always arrive here once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.96,0:03:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand the reason why that is true?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.34,0:04:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is because you are afraid to admit the reality of their deaths.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.18,0:04:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that shipwreck incident, you were the only one to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.40,0:04:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Big Brod'er!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.24,0:04:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Help me, Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.49,0:04:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sonia!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.70,0:04:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Julien!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.99,0:04:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Big Brod'er!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.45,0:04:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sonia!! Julien!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.55,0:04:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Because I am alive, my family must also be alive."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.56,0:04:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is what you are thinking. Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.56,0:04:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you are the only one destiny has chosen!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.10,0:04:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your family is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.23,0:05:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who are unable to accept reality will never be able to understand the answers of their destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.90,0:05:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you accept your fate, you will begin to see those answers unfold in due time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.99,0:05:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come along. It is now time for you to clarify it with your own hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.70,0:05:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That your family is sleeping within this cemetery!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.60,0:05:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you wish to leave this place, you must confirm it with your very own hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.82,0:05:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't right...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.69,0:06:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not possible! Rafael's family was supposed to have gone missing...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.01,0:06:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rafael, everything begins from here on out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.93,0:06:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.44,0:07:11.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Activate it! Your fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.04,0:07:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave yourself for the darkness of your heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.42,0:07:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then absorb and surpass it, Rafael.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.09,0:07:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The answer of your destiny lies just beyond that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.58,0:08:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deathscythe!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.00,0:08:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Monster the darkness in your heart created.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.18,0:08:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, my destiny was decided that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.52,0:08:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Assimilating myself to the darkness of my heart and then giving myself to it is what saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.44,0:08:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Saved you"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.11,0:08:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why don't you want to send your Monsters to the Graveyard that much?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.16,0:08:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you gave yourself to your destiny, then that should be indifferent to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.20,0:08:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nameless Pharaoh, what exactly do know of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.33,0:08:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I {\i1}do{\i0} know! You don't want to put your Monsters through the same pain your family suffered!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.55,0:08:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you fear the Graveyard so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.80,0:08:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the real you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.63,0:08:55.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.47,0:09:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have succumbed to the darkness in my heart long ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.22,0:09:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot return after all this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.28,0:09:12.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can finally see them again...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.74,0:09:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.62,0:09:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Underworld - Heaven Circle removes every Monster Card in our decks from the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.58,0:09:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And each player can Summon from the Graveyard one Monster every turn without Summoning Conditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.92,0:09:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When activated, All Monsters on the field are destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.55,0:09:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Black Magician Girl was destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.84,0:09:39.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So why is Deathscythe the only one left...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.89,0:09:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By sacrificing one card from my hand, Deathscythe is revived.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.22,0:09:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the one who decides that is not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.89,0:09:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.73,0:09:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deathscythe is revived by its own will!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.73,0:09:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.57,0:09:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even I can no longer remove Deathscythe.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.57,0:09:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.86,0:10:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Monster that can't be destroyed...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.28,0:10:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as Deathscythe is on the field, the player cannot Summon a new Monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.79,0:10:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're saying that it's not possible to bring your Monsters back from the Cemetery?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.75,0:10:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I told you before that I can no longer return!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.59,0:10:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My destiny now lies with Deathscythe!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.14,0:10:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I will leave myself to this destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.10,0:10:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deathscythe... This is the darkness of your heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.02,0:10:31.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't defeat this thing, Rafael... You'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.98,0:10:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Due to the effects of Underworld - Heaven Circle, I Special Summon Black Magician from the Graveyard in Attack Position!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.86,0:10:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's revived the dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.24,0:10:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi still has a chance if he can Summon Monsters from the Graveyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.29,0:10:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set a card face-down and end my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.71,0:10:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! I draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.88,0:10:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of Underworld - Heaven Circle's effects, I Special Summon Jack's Knight in Attack Position!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.84,0:11:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can even Summon Monsters from the Graveyard during your opponent's turn?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.72,0:11:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nameless Pharaoh!! Engrave the darkness of my heart into your soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.14,0:11:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deathscythe attacks your Black Magician!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.35,0:11:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forbidden Requiem!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.94,0:11:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reverse card, open! Gravity Release!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.70,0:11:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This card changes the Battle Position of all the Monsters on the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.66,0:11:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sweet! If all the Monsters on his field are in Defense Mode, there ain't gonna be a battle at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.55,0:11:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so sure of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.05,0:11:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.17,0:11:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reverse card, open! Death End of Hunting Soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.14,0:11:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I change the Battle Position of one of my Monsters on the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.10,0:11:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And destroy all the Defense Monsters on my opponent's side of the field!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.52,0:11:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.87,0:12:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.08,0:12:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-He killed his two Monsters with almost no effort...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.50,0:12:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.46,0:12:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.96,0:12:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Due to the effects of Underworld - Heaven Circle, I Special Summon Black Magician Girl from the Graveyard!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.39,0:12:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then I activate Altar of Resurrection from my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.31,0:12:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I remove two cards from the top of my deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.98,0:12:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I return one card from the Graveyard into my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.23,0:12:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the card I choose will be the Eye of Timaeus!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.95,0:12:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I combine Timaeus with Black Magician Girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.12,0:12:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show yourself, Dragon Knight Black Magician Girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.04,0:13:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's Special Effect holds the power to destroy one of the opponent's Monsters in exchange for a card in your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.88,0:13:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, that won't work against Deathscythe!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.47,0:13:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll move on to attack Deathscythe with Dragon Knight Black Magician Girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.51,0:13:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Dragon Burst!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.11,0:13:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did it work?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.45,0:13:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You cannot defeat Deathscythe!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.41,0:13:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But why, Yugi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.16,0:13:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even though you know attacking Deathscythe is pointless...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.83,0:13:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I place a card face-down, ending my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.79,0:13:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you're set on stupid things like trying to change the heart of your opponent,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.17,0:13:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}you'll wind up losing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.67,0:13:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.80,0:13:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I launch the effects of Underworld - Heaven Circle!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.14,0:13:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'll Special Summon Queen's Knight from my Cemetery into Attack Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.56,0:13:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to discard the card I draw in this turn...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.48,0:14:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and activate Sealing Sword of the Orichalcos!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.16,0:14:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This will rid Timaeus of its Special Effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.53,0:14:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deathscythe!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.70,0:14:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack Dragon Knight Black Magician Girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.79,0:14:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forbidden Requiem!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.79,0:14:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-Yugi!\N -Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.46,0:14:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This finishes it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.60,0:14:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.72,0:14:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activated Reduction Barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.27,0:14:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This card makes it so the battle damage a player receives is only 1/10.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.23,0:14:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He saved himself...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.77,0:14:46.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But now he's only got 10 Life Points...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.53,0:14:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.65,0:14:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This won't end yet, Rafael!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.74,0:14:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't ever give up until my Life Points hit zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.49,0:14:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you not see it, Nameless Pharaoh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.08,0:14:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The game has already been settled.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.12,0:15:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I thought, destiny has been determined!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.92,0:15:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That destiny...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.63,0:15:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Along with the darkness in your heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.13,0:15:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to destroy it when I kill that monster over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.39,0:15:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.10,0:15:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Due to the effects of Underworld - Heaven Circle, I Special Summon Big Shield Gardna from the Graveyard in Defense Position!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.98,0:15:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I then activate Pot of Greed from my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.40,0:15:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I draw two cards from my deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.53,0:15:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So I finally got you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.90,0:15:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll activate the Magic Card called Spider Web from my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.08,0:15:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It allows me to add one card sent to the opponent's Cemetery in the previous turn into my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.04,0:15:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you playing at?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.29,0:15:49.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The card you sent to your Cemetery one turn ago was Resurrection of the Dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.05,0:15:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're not able to light it, then I'll do it for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.13,0:15:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The light of your heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.97,0:15:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.43,0:15:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do... Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.39,0:16:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I revive Guardian Eatos from the Cemetery!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.45,0:16:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eatos...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.78,0:16:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi revived Eatos...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.08,0:16:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.20,0:16:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And from my hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.41,0:16:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1}, lend me your strength...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.63,0:16:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate The Claw of Hermos!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.01,0:16:39.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi, Yugi's... using your... your Hermos!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.10,0:16:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hermos will fuse with Queen's Knight!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.02,0:16:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I equip the Equipment Magic, Saint Bow of Goddess - Artemis, to Eatos!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.36,0:16:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her Attack Power goes up by 2500 points!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.78,0:16:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deathscythe loses 500 Attack Points because Eatos is no longer in the Graveyard!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.79,0:17:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their Attack Points are equal!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.45,0:17:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you planning to have them kill each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.50,0:17:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you {\i1}do{\i0}, Deathscythe won't die!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.46,0:17:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Destiny will {\i1}not{\i0} change!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.09,0:17:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think back, Rafael.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.26,0:17:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Monsters and the bonds you shared with your family!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.80,0:17:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\an8}Isn't this Guardian Eatos?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.76,0:17:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\an8}Julien and me worked really hard to find this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.93,0:17:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those bonds hold the power to {\i1}change{\i0} destiny!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.89,0:17:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sonia!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.77,0:17:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Congrats!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.95,0:17:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eatos, attack Deathscythe!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.70,0:17:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forbidden Song!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.79,0:17:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate the effect of Saint Bow Goddess - Artemis!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.25,0:17:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In battle, when the opponent's Monster activated a Special Effect,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.71,0:17:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can ignore the battle damage and continue attacking!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.05,0:17:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,WHAT?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.60,0:18:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see! If the opponent's hand reaches zero, Deathscythe won't revive!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.24,0:18:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,EATOS!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.04,0:18:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I figured as much. Eatos was the one you called at the very end.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.92,0:18:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You weren't able to truly become one with the darkness in your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.09,0:18:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In reality, you were just lonely from the fact that your family went missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.39,0:18:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to escape from the solitude, you began to rely on Dartz and his made up "destiny".
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.35,0:18:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The darkness of your heart was an illusion you created.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.82,0:18:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your fate hasn't been decided for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.99,0:18:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're supposed to open it {\i1}yourself{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.28,0:19:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But The Barrier of Orichalcos takes the soul of the loser without prejudice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.20,0:19:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That, at least, is one fact you cannot deny.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.71,0:19:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rafael!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.13,0:19:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.17,0:19:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of Underworld - Heaven Circle, I Special Summon Guardian Grarl from my Cemetery.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.59,0:19:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monsters from your Graveyard...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.30,0:19:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I activate Soul Charge from my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.72,0:19:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It allows me to Special Summon the Monsters from my Cemetery.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.56,0:19:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So the guy's still after Yugi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.90,0:19:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, the Monsters revived by Soul Charge can't attack this turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.03,0:19:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So then... What's Rafael trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.49,0:19:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now there is no longer any Monsters in the Cemetery...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.66,0:19:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I'm at ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.79,0:19:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rafael... You...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.91,0:19:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the effect of Soul Charge, I take 500 points of damage to my Life for each Monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.34,0:20:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rafael!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.65,0:20:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eatos...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.41,0:20:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eatos! All of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.62,0:20:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I caught you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.91,0:20:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I caught ya, bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.37,0:20:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.58,0:20:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Big Brod'er!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.82,0:21:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rafael!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.24,0:21:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The barrier disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.74,0:21:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.24,0:21:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Did you pull it off, Yugi?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.16,0:21:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why? Why wasn't my soul taken?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.42,0:21:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Barrier of Orichalcos is the manifestation of the darkness in its user's heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.26,0:21:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The darkness in my heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.84,0:21:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's why... I should be...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.09,0:21:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The darkness of your heart is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.26,0:21:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The darkness in my heart... disappeared?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.44,0:21:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.15,0:21:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.27,0:22:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The houses lined down the street drifting by being dyed red
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.63,0:22:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I notice pain, it'll turn into happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.24,0:22:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Every time people wipe away tears, they understand bonds
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.31,0:22:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The warm strength that you gave me will change into kindness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.79,0:22:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Overflowing feelings don't stop
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.07,0:22:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll live while I feel it, for me to be myself
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.97,0:22:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Healed by overflowing friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.12,0:23:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Our fated encounter is a truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.64,0:23:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and someday we'll be able to understand each other
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.08,0:23:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rafael's barrier disappeared?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.29,0:23:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So The Barrier of Orichalcos is really the darkness of its user's heart, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.50,0:23:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The location where Dartz hides was given to us by Rafael,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.42,0:23:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so we head to the temple of Doma after the destruction of Paradias.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.22,0:23:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then suddenly a swarm of unidentified soldiers surround the helicopter we're riding.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.52,0:23:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they goons as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.81,0:23:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this also Doma's doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.19,0:23:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.98,0:23:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"To the Final Battlefield!\N Dartz VS Yugi and Kaiba"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.02,0:23:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel standby!
